  "text": "All three structures were refined using Refmac5 (40) and Phenix [CITATION_1] . The final model of [GC(8-BrG)GCGGC] 2 was refined without restraints and with anisotropic temperature factors. The last few cycles of the [GC(8-BrG)GC GGC] 2 refinement were performed using all data, including the R free set. The other two models, GCGGC GGC and GC(8-BrG)GCGGCGGC, were refined using isotropic B-factors.",
